      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 specifies a single standardized compression-bending load configuration. Only one load angle (10°) and one fixation torque (nominal per IFU) were tested, limiting coverage of the clinical use space. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3; noted as gap but accepted given regulatory precedent for F1717 single-condition testing."
